front.title: •I Have A Really Bad Feeling About This
front.gametext: If opponent just initiated a battle where opponent has more than double your power, target your highest-ability character in that battle. Draw destiny. If destiny < target's ability, deploy one character there from hand (for free).
front.lore: 'I'm rather embarrassed, General Solo, but it appears you are to be the main course at a banquet in my honor.'
